Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:07.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Take back the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji returns to the silver screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.18,0:00:18.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And we give you loyal anime watchers a sneak peek!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.82,0:00:22.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Mikoko, the leading (and only) lady of the Kaiji anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:26.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ever since her introduction, she's been popular among those in the know online!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:30.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Instead of her, the leading lady of Kaiji 2 will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:33.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuriko Yoshitaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:39.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,She plays the daughter of Ishida, who lost his life in the first movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:49.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They were all so frank that there were no misunderstandings at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:53.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The rest of the cast were fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.31,0:01:01.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And the fantastic setting is intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:06.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I really enjoyed the characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:10.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's the secret of the new game!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:15.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji 2: Jinsei Dakkai Game, this November 5th!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:20.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,究極のモンスターマシンの本丸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:23.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji challenges the demonic trays, core of the Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:25.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔性の３段クルーンに挑むカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:28.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけー！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:26.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:36.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フロア全体を沼と逆方向に傾ける\N奇想天外 空前絶後の奇策！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.43,0:01:32.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He tilts the floor itself in the opposite direction of the Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:35.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,An unprecedented, unique plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:38.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに対し 一条は何と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:42.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But Ichijou tilts the Bog to match the floor's tilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:44.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼をフロアと同じ方向に傾き返す\N傾斜かぶせで抗う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.44,0:01:45.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{dongs}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:46.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必死の攻防！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:50.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの残金は200万\N500発を切る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:50.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji now has only two million left! Only 500 shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.89,0:01:54.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,迫る破滅 壊滅の時！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:54.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's doom closes in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:58.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,策と策 執念と執念の激突！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:59.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Their tricks, their determination clash!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:03.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,550)\pos(640,505)}A Sure Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:31.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please... I don't need a lot of luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:31.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む　強運なんかじゃ\Nなくっていい！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:53.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not looking for a miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:57.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奇跡も要らない　平運！\N起こってくれよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit... I just need one thing to go my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:03:03.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごく普通の現象！確率！\N起きてくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:01.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just make things happen how they normally should!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:02.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please, make it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:12.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… ダメ ダーメ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:12.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:15.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,台を叩くのは御法度だぜ\Nカイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:17.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You should know that striking the machine is against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:20.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってるはずだろ？\Nフフフ… とんだ悪あがき
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:21.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's not going to do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:23.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせえ　黙ってろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:23.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ勝負はついてねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:24.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:29.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついてねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:37.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ… どうしたどうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:39.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？カイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クッ… ふざけるな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:44.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Give me a break! This isn't the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:47.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終わってたまるか！このまま…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:49.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It can't end like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:49.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終われるかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll hit the jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:51.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出す！出すんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:54.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I'll hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:56.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何としても 出す！クソッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:58.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Dammit! This makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:58.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるかよ こんなことって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:02.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで いくつにも\N積み上げた仕掛け
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:02.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've done so much to make sure this goes my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:06.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ちの仕組みを\N念入りに積み上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:06.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've planned out every last detail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:12.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが 結局は\N不遇 流れ アンラッキー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:12.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But everything's going his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:14.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなもののために\N消えるっていうのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:15.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Will that be my end!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:05:00.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あった！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:04.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見える！一筋の光明！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:03.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He sees it! A ray of hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:10.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This will be my victory! My sure path to the jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:06.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな所に勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:11.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ちへの確実な道があった！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありやがった！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:12.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:15.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てる！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:17.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can win! This is how I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:19.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままなら 勝てる！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:21.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But! But!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:21.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが しかし！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:30.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あー\Nクソッ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Aw shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:36.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,切れた\Nああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:36.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:47.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… 終わっちまった\Nカイジさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:50.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:50.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくん…\Nカイジさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:01.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヒ イヒ イヒ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:21.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪運尽きたな カイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Looks like your luck's run out, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:30.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:32.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お帰りだ　ハハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:38.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Someone give me a hand. He's probably too shocked to stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:37.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手伝ってやれ　どうやら\Nショックで足腰が立たないらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:42.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:44.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:48.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰が言ったよ？終了なんてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:48.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Who said I was done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:49.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:51.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくん\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:07:00.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハ… からっけつが！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:02.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The suitcase is empty! You're out of money, you're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終わりなんだよ 金がなくなりゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:07.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's how casinos work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それがカジノの鉄則だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:09.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前はもう客じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:11.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're not a guest anymore! You're just broke trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:11.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただの文無しのクズなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:15.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Trash! Trash trash trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:15.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズ！クズ！クズ！クズ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰れ 地下へ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Back in your hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:20.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ？虫ケラめ オケラ 文無し！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:21.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You penniless worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金なら…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.06,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've got some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:30.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've got some more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:31.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金なら ある！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ？金はあるだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:33.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You have money?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:43.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,トイレだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm taking a leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:45.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:47.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいな まだ終わっちゃいねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:49.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone else touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:50.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰にも触らせるな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジくん！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:52.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:55.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん 遠藤さんも\Nちょっといいか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Pops. Endoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:57.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ？あ… ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:10.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:12.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金を貸せってんじゃあるまいな？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you want to borrow more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:15.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるまいなって それ以外何が…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:15.20,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What else would I even—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:17.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言っとくがもう金はない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:20.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうこれ以上 貸せる金なんざ\Nびた一文…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:20.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't have anything left to lend to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:24.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっちの男が持ってるカバン\Nあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:22.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How about the money in that bag he's holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金だろ　額は1000万
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:27.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's money. Probably about ten million.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:30.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\Nこの賭けに負けた時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:33.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You've got it so you can bail out the second I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:33.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐ逃げられるように\N用意した金が入ってるんだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:35.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部 知ってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:35.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I know exactly what you're up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:39.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼む　貸してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:39.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Please! Lend me that money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:45.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ あんただって\N破滅だ！遠藤さん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:45.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I lose here, your goose is cooked too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:52.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな！疫病神が！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:51.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're jinxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冗談じゃねえ！突っ込めるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:54.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you just fucking with me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:58.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この金は 俺の最後の命綱！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This money is my last lifeline!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:01.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつで高飛びしなきゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I don't have it ready to ditch with...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:03.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってるのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:02.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You know what's waiting for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:08.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hell on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:10.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地獄じゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな命銭を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:20.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You think I'm going to give up that lifeline to a luckless loser like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:20.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おめえみてえなクズの能なし
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:26.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You made it to the critical moment! All you needed was one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:23.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この肝心要 勝負所で
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:26.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただの１発 １発だぞ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:31.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１発だけだ！それすら\N決めることのできないゴミ野郎に
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:33.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's all you needed, but you blew it! You think I have any more money to waste on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つぎ込めるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I was a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカだった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:46.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の口車に乗った俺が
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:49.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I was a complete fool to listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:49.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカだった… 情けねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:55.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あばよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:00.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Endoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:02.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠藤さん…\N幕は下りたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:02.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's curtains for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:08.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つけたんだよ　勝つ道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:07.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've found a path to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確実な勝利を
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:10.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A sure winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:30.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この上 何を企んでいやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:29.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What is he planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:34.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… それ 本当か？カイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:33.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Really, Kaiji!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:36.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今さらウソついてどうすんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Would I lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:39.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでもまだ逃げ出す気か？\N遠藤さん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:39.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to run away now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:45.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰ってこい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰ってこい！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:47.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:50.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:49.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Endoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:57.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can't back out of this fight now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:57.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負だろ！ここでいかずに\Nどうするよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ボケたか？遠藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:59.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:07.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're inches away! Inches away from 700 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:04.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てるんだよ あと数センチ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,数センチで７億に届く！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:09.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くるとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:10.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no guarantee it'll pay out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:12.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限らねえだろ\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:16.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord6}Even if you're telling the truth, there's no guarantee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:16.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の話が本当だとしても\Nくるとは限らねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:20.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何言ってんだよ\N今やろうとしてることは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:18.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord6}What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:26.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord6}It's as sure as spinning the lottery until there's only one ball left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:22.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ってみれば福引きのガラガラを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:26.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の玉まで回そうって\N言ってるようなもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:28.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's guaranteed to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:29.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ずだ！絶対 当たる！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:34.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It may be guaranteed, but there's no guarantee it'll happen in ten million!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:34.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その｢必ず｣が 俺のこの1000万で\Nくるとは限らねえだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:37.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right, Kaiji!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:37.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ？そうだろうが カイジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:41.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外れ 失敗する可能性も\Nあるだろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:40.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It can still fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:43.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,抜かすな！\Nうっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:42.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:47.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,屁みたいなこと\N言ってんじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:47.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't pussy out like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:52.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It could fail? So what!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:50.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外れる？失敗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それがどうした！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:55.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If it wails, we may be sunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:55.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沈めばいいだろ そん時は！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:58.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そん時は 地の底暮らしもアリだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:58.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But we can keep living, sunk in the earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:00.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You need to be willing to put that on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:02.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚悟しろよ そのぐらい！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:03.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Plus...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:07.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第一 今を逃げられたとして
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:08.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if you run away, what happens then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:09.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その後は？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:14.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借金取りを恐れて 外国でひたすら\N息を潜めて過ごすってか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:14.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you just gonna hide from the loan sharks in some foreign country?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:16.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is that all you want out of life!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいのかよ それで？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:26.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's in it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:29.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何がある？そうやって逃げた先に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:35.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All you'll be able to do is drink your money away while you wait to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:32.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,酒びたりで\N虎の子の金を食い潰して
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:35.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな半ボケの人生が関の山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:39.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな未来があんたの望みかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:38.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is that the future you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:44.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違うだろ？あんたの望む未来は\Nそんなんじゃないだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:44.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It isn't, right? You don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:47.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かれよ 遠藤さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:49.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, Endoh! Listen to me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:49.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってくれよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:52.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Follow that ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:53.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,迷ったら 望みだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:55.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That ray of hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:55.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,希望だろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:03.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Life is only really worth living when you have hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:05.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,希望に進むのが\N気持ちのいい人生ってもんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:11.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if we sink into that hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:08.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:11.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地の底に 沈もうともだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:31.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠藤さん 聞いてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:31.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen to this, Endoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:39.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,約束しよう\Nもし地に沈むことになったら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.13,0:13:36.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:39.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we end up trapped in that hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:46.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Every month, on payday, I'll buy you two beers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:48.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,毎月 給料日に\Nビールを２本 振る舞おう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:50.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠藤さんが くたばるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Every month until you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:20.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Make it three.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:21.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３本だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:23.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Three beers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:25.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,缶ビール３本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:27.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Three and it's a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:29.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,約束したぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:31.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 分かった！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:36.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:39.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て！\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:39.69,kaiji-dialog-herp,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs42}／人◕ ‿‿ ◕人＼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:40.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:42.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借用書\Nええっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:43.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now, of all times!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:44.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな時に？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:46.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:46.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな時もクソもあるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:51.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:53.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…ったく
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら これでいいだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:55.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here, are you happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry I don't have a chop with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:58.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハンコは持ってたよな？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:00.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:01.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ行くぜ\Nあんまり間を空けて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:03.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't want them to decide I'm not coming back and let someone else play.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:04.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,棄権にされちゃ たまらねえからな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:11.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ あのガキは？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:10.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's with that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:15.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,追いつめられてるくせに\N逆に生き生きしてやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:15.42,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now that he's well and truly fucked, he brightens up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:18.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼りになるんだか ならねえんだか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:18.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't even know if that makes him reliable or a flake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Endoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:21.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠藤はん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:24.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言っても始まらねえ\Nここまで来たら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:24.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no point in even talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:29.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All we can do now is rely on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう託すしかねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:29.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:43.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Ichijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:42.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待たせたな 一条
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:50.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This time I'll finish the Bog off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:51.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度こそ そいつの\N息の根を止めるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:52.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,With this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:00.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すでに5000万を溶かし
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Having burned through 50 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:05.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに1000万 合計6000万！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:04.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji adds another 10 million! His total bet is 60 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:10.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見物人の誰しもが抱く\N狂気の沙汰！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:09.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No one in the audience expected this crazy move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:14.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Where did you get that money, you son of a bitch!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:14.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様… その金 どうやって？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:25.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃんは？\N気分が悪いんで少し休むとよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:21.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Where's pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:24.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's not feeling that hot, so he's taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:29.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Can't expect his nerves to hold through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪くもなるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:30.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通の神経ならな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:35.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now you, doing this with a grin on your face... You I don't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:33.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この修羅場で生き生きしてる\Nお前の神経のほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:37.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうかしてんだよ\N別に生き生きなんかしてねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not exactly enjoying myself here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:40.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その金 あんたが？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You lent him that money!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:43.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:45.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっ 貸さざるを得なくなってな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:48.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカなことを！無駄金だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:48.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Are you insane? You're throwing it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かもしれねえ… が
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:53.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But if I give up now, I won't be able to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:54.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで下がっても見えねえのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:57.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That ray of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:57.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,希望ってやつがさ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:59.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:16:59.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ その金がラスト
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:02.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで正真正銘 すっからかん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:02.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,My honest-to-goodness bottom dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:08.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しのぎゃ 今度こそ勝ちだよ\Nあんたの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:06.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Survive it, and you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:11.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だよ そのあからさまな\N迷惑顔は？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:11.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you making that face for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:16.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm a valued guest as long as I have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:13.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも客商売か？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:17.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金を持ってきた以上 俺たちは客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:20.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's how casinos work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:21.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カジノの鉄則だろ　歓迎しろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:24.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now get me another ten million Paqy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:24.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,交換だ　パッキー1000万
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:27.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:28.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:32.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この金 調べさせてもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:32.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We need to check that money first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:34.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だと？何を今さら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:34.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:39.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Check him for magnets, too, he's been gone too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ！それと磁気チェックだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:38.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらくフロアを出たんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:41.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌なら台に座ることは許さない！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:41.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're getting checked before you touch that machine again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:52.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji undergoes another magnet check on Ichijou's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:48.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,有無を言わせぬ一条の言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:52.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 再び磁気チェックを受ける
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:58.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ichijou himself spends ten minutes checking the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:56.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに一条 自ら札束をチェック
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:18:00.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10分が経過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:01.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How is this happening!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:03.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何てこった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:06.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought it was over! Now there's more!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:07.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終わったと思ったら予想外の延長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:12.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I survived the last round, but there's no guarantee I'll be so lucky this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:10.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきは何とかしのいだが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:12.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この1000万も\Nしのげるとは限らない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:19.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クッ… 時間を稼がないと
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:24.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I need to buy time until my ultimate weapon—my trump card—arrives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:24.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが…\N最終兵器 切り札が届くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:24.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:26.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:29.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もういいだろ\Nいつまで待たせるつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:29.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna keep me waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:32.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前みたいなチンピラが\N急に用意した金だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:36.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can never be too careful about money a thug like you comes up with out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:36.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怪しいに決まってる！\N慎重になるのも当たり前だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:41.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい 元は俺の金だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:40.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's my money you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:42.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:43.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を企んでる？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:46.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're stalling. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:46.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,長引かせて 何か企んでるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:48.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バッ バカ言え！もう少し待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:49.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course not! Just hold on a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,店長\N何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:54.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実は さっきまで沼の横で見ていて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:56.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've been watching from the side of the Bog, and I think I noticed something...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:57.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つ 気になったことが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:02.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:04.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かか？\N偶然とも思えません
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:04.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Now that I think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:09.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえば…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:19.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I knew it! Lady Luck is on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:19.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり 運は俺にある！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:22.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The heavens smile upon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:24.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天が味方した　勝てる！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:28.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't even need the remote to finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:29.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最終リモコンを待たず\N押し切れる！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:36.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Very well. Let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:36.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かった\N受ければいいんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:38.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,交換してやれ\Nはっ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Give him his Paqy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:38.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:45.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの野郎 急に態度が\N変わりやがった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:44.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Something changed his mind quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:47.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌な予感がしねえか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:51.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へへへ　構わねえさ そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:51.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't give a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:54.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ともかく さっさと\N座っちまうこった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:54.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to sit right down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:58.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right at the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:58.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつの前に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:09.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よう 帰ってきたぜ　悪魔め
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:09.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yo. I'm back, you devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:13.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい 戻ってきた\Nカイジだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:11.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey! He's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:12.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:18.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:15.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん！\Nカイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:17.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん\Nカイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:19.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:22.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:20.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:32.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,虫ケラが！へへへ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:29.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That maggot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:41.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ カイジ カイジ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:41.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:43.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうぞ\Nああ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:52.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right, let's roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:53.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて いくか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:57.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ カイジ カイジ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:03.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ラスト1000万
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:02.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,My last ten million...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:10.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 一条　それぞれの\N勝利への確信が交差する
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:13.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and Ichijou's belief they will win intermingles in a final battle beyond all limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:13.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限界を超えた 最終決戦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:21.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オラー！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:22.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They crash together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:26.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突入！突入！突入！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:27.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They crash! They crash!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:35.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Proverbs of Kaiji Returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:45.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Listen to me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:51.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Follow that ray! That ray of hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:58.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Life is only really worth living when you have hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:03.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even if we sink into that hell!
